data.description: Enjoy the majestic views from this 1-acre lot in Meadview Unit 2, located between Lake Mead and the Grand Wash Cliffs, a hidden little treasure in Northwestern Arizona. This three-bedroom two-bath home has the Main bedroom/bath at one end of the home and the two additional guests  bedrooms and additional bath at the other end. It has a New Metal Roof, New windows, New Flooring, New Farm Kitchen Sink, New Fixtures and New AC unit. Enjoy the casual dining and open floor plan with the oversized great room for entertainment of family and friends. The kitchen has an island with a breakfast sitting bar. The 24D x 32W 2-car garage will help with the storage of your car or recreational vehicles. Property is graded with desert landscaping and a small outdoor workshop or storage shed. Enjoy the shade and view of the Grand Wash Cliffs from the front covered deck and back patio with covered sitting area. Camping, horses, and some livestock are permitted. Located just a short distance from downtown Meadview where you will find local restaurants, gift shops, VFW, Beauty shop, Nail shop, and Gas n Grub. If Las Vegas or Laughlin are places you like to visit for extra entertainment and fun, they are about 2 hours away. Or take a drive through the Joshua Tree National Forest on your way to the Grand Canyon Skywalk about 40 minutes away. If four wheeling is your joy bring your favorite dirt toys to explore all surrounding trails or visit Lake Mead for all your favorite water sports. As a member of our Property Owners Association, you can enjoy all the Amenities of our local MCA, which include access to the solar heated Community Pool, Putt-Putt Golf Course, indoor and outdoor shuffleboard, Pool Tables, Ping Pong, and Tennis/Pickleball Courts and Bingo on Fridays.
